WEBVTT

00:00:26.624 --> 00:00:31.549
Ali za početak ću da vam ispričam priču
g. Ričarda Mesine,

00:00:31.573 --> 00:00:34.702
koji je moj prijatelj
i direktor osnovne škole.

00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:37.167
Jednog dana je primio telefonski poziv.

00:00:39.279 --> 00:00:40.430
Sagovornik je rekao:

00:00:40.454 --> 00:00:44.336
"G. Mesina, moj sin Džoni
neće doći u školu danas

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:45.823
jer je bolestan."

00:00:46.498 --> 00:00:48.234
G. Mesina je pitao:

00:00:48.258 --> 00:00:50.272
"Izvinite, s kim razgovaram?"

00:00:50.788 --> 00:00:52.278
A sagovornik je rekao:

00:00:52.302 --> 00:00:53.967
"Ja sam moj otac."

00:00:53.991 --> 00:00:56.778
(Smeh)

00:00:58.227 --> 00:00:59.909
Dakle, ova priča -

00:00:59.933 --> 00:01:01.465
(Smeh)